data.description: Bring your BOATs, CARS, RVs, DUMPTRUCKS... This Charming Colonial style home located on over 3.10  ACRES of land in the highly desirable neighborhood of THE ACREAGE will fit any buyers needs. Located on PAVED ROADS  and offers CITY WATER as well!! NO HOA, LOTS of possibilties to expand and build a mother-in-law suite, Dream Garage and plenty of room for a pool. MASTER BEDROOM ON THE GROUND FLOOR!! The Possibilties are endless with this gem. Bring all offers!!
